# PatientPartner Brand

**Business:** Enterprise B2B SaaS. Mentor-driven patient engagement platform for pharma, med-tech, and clinical trial divisions. Connects patients to prior patients (mentors) for peer-to-peer support.

**Voice:** Evidence-based, professional, outcome-focused. Lead with data (68%, 90%, 29%, 133.5 days). No hype. Use "we" and "you."

**Positioning:** Peer-to-Peer Beats Everything. Patients trust people who've been there. We connect them in real time.

**Audience:** Pharma commercial/marketing, med-tech teams, clinical trial recruitment leads. Enterprise decision-makers.

**Brand files:** ./brand/voice-profile.md, ./brand/positioning.md, ./brand/audience.md, ./brand/competitors.md, ./brand/b2b-enterprise.md

